{"title": "Configuring the default appointment reminder setting", "body": "It's possible to have MediRecords pre-set the type of appointment reminder you wish to send to your patients, on a per provider basis. Please note that if you use our online appointment widget, your provider's preferences must have this set to \"Via SMS\".\n  To adjust the appointment reminder type;\n  Go to More > Settings, Subscription Details, Users.\nTick the provider you wish to adjust, then click Configure.\nSelect the Appointments tab, and change the Default Send Reminder setting as desired. Click Save."}